<p>Contact information for the Department for Transportâ€™s media office.</p>

<p>Journalists should call our central newsdesk on 020 7944 3021.</p>

<p>This media-only line operates from Monday to Friday, 8am to 7pm. For urgent media enquiries outside of these hours, please call 020 7944 4292.</p>

<p>If you are not a member of the media, contact either the general enquiries switchboard on 0300 330 3000 or <a rel="external" href="https://forms.dft.gov.uk/contact-dft-and-agencies/">use the online system</a>.</p>

